==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: event horizon
<hw>e*vent" ho*ri"zon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physics,
Astron.)</fld> <def>the boundary surface surrounding a <er>black
hole</er>, from outside of which nothing inside can be observed, because
nothing inside that surface, even light, can escape beyond it. See also
<er>black hole</er> and <er>escape velocity</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eventilate</ent>⟦br⟧
